keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map <a-F> LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map I passNextKey
unmap zH
map 0 scrollToLeft
unmap zL
map $ scrollToRight
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap >>
map gK moveTabRight
unmap <<
map gJ moveTabLeft
unmap p
unmap P
map P LinkHints.activateModeToOpenIncognito
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
unmap ^
map % visitPreviousTab
map R reload hard
